title: Abraham Lincoln: A History (Volume 1)
creator: John Hay and John George Nicolay
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Abraham Lincoln: A History (Volume 1) by John Hay and John George Nicolay. This is the biography of Abraham Lincoln, written by two of his private secretaries. (Summary by ashleighjane) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B Part 1 (172MB) Download M4B Part 2 (190MB)
